echo "
You must restart pa-applet (or restart your Desktop Manager).
For pop sound to work on volume change, make sure event sounds are enabled in your Desktop Manager.
Test with the following command: canberra-gtk-play -i audio-volume-change
In XFCE settings: Appearance > Settings, Enable event sounds
See also: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Libcanberra
"
}
